Definition: any shrub of the genus Cotoneaster: erect or creeping shrubs having richly colored autumn foliage and many small white to pinkish flowers followed by tiny red or black fruits
Synonyms: shrub, genus_Cotoneaster, m, any, of, the, genus, Cotoneaster, erect, or, creeping, shrubs, having, richly, colored, autumn, foliage, and, many, small, white, to, pinkish, flowers, followed, by, tiny, red, black, fruits
Category: noun.plant
